{"type":"answer","id":8656,"parentType":"question","parentId":1849,"uid":15,"contents":"他们的观点还是有一点对的。<br>\n<br>\n君子有三戒：<br>\n少之时，血气未定，戒之在色；<br>\n及其壮也，血气方刚，戒之在斗；<br>\n及其老也，血气既衰，戒之在得。<br>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ----《论语》","date":"2019-02-04","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":2}